{"tid":929149,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"【最cool主子】港版不爽貓教反貪？大學生拍片創意大爆發","createTime":"2018-12-05T11:11:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T11:55:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ec1c107c5c8560c8c49600268eadba27e342fa69","tid":929149,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:11:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181205/20561239\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181205%2F20561239&d=OessR97wZcg0TsqPXAmbnNWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=77041818\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181205%2F20561239&h=1436ae46\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181205/20561239</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年12月05日 <br />\n<br />\n【最cool主子】港版不爽貓教反貪？大學生拍片創意大爆發<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181204/large/1543931373_e073.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181204%2Flarge%2F1543931373_e073.jpg&h=7c9d8c8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【特約報道】「香港，勝在有ICAC！」是大家耳熟能詳的口號，作為香港人，我們都會為這個城市擁有廉潔的法治而驕傲，因為法治正正就是令一個地方穩定、安全和有保障的基石。很多新一代未必知道，香港在六、七十年代曾經是貪污受賄非常嚴重的一個地方，而ICAC的成立致力打擊貪污，令香港逐漸成為廉潔之都。廉政公署社區關係處（社關處）早前聯同香港理工大學及浸會大學廣告系學生，合作製作出一系列反貪廣告宣傳片。以年青人的角度去思考和創作，讓新一代能夠得到共鳴，了解廉潔對社會發展的重要性。<br />\n<br />\n社關處更挑選了其中一個作品《不爽貓》的創作理念延伸，拍攝了由林雪參演的網片。不爽貓本是在外國網絡上瘋傳的一隻貓咪，牠因為無論任何時候都帶着一副不爽的表情，吸引了大批網民關注，令知名度大增。不爽貓的特點激發了同學們的創作思維︰在不當的利益和好處前面，我們都應該像不爽貓一樣，保持不爽的態度，對貪污堅決零容忍。<br />\n<br />\n參與創作的同學們坦言本身對貪污受賄的概念並不是很清晰，但通過這次創作，在資料搜集和討論的過程當中不但激發起他們的正義感，更對反貪有更深入的了解和體會；當社會失去了公義，當社會不再廉潔，我們便會失去了一個可靠、安穩的社會，這絕對不會是大家所嚮往的一種生活。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181204/large/1543931374_7803.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181204%2Flarge%2F1543931374_7803.jpg&h=568ac30a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《不爽貓》無論面對任何情況都帶着一副不爽的表情。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181204/large/1543931424_298d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181204%2Flarge%2F1543931424_298d.jpg&h=33863dc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港理工大學設計學院學生分享《不爽貓》的創作心得。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181204/large/1543931426_4ed7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181204%2Flarge%2F1543931426_4ed7.jpg&h=5788624f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾錦程（香港理工大學設計學院高級專任導師）認為學生們在創作過程當中相當認真，能發揮自己的創意和提出不一樣的想法。<br />\n<br />\n欣賞更多學生創作短片： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2yXgFfM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2yXgFfM&d=OessR97wZcg0TsqPXAmbnNWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=0d4b715a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2yXgFfM</a>  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n房價浮動　應自行比較各平台<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n海關跟進　律師：可民事索償"},{"pid":"06d1438fce8633ef4fff648e372978b76437dcf0","tid":929149,"uid":117602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:50:53.000Z","msg":"ICAC <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c274855cd8b6313f3938a60e95b97ec86f0ac2","tid":929149,"uid":35382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:51:33.000Z","msg":"左2 pure 右2大波波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acbef90a7d51adb1107f9d9dfe2639e92ae2f853","tid":929149,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"